title: Dim Sum Shop - Dizengoff Center
typeOfFood: Chinese, Fast food, Take-out, Kosher, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This branch is inside the southern half of the mall, one floor above street entrance. The dim sum is made without oil or frying or preservatives. Several types of vegetable dim sum. Small with a few tables. Also sells frozen dim sum and steamer baskets to take home.
